FOREVER MISS PICKLES (WITH ART) 
 TIMELESS ADVICE ON AGING 
 HOW COMPUTERS CONNECT FAMILIES 
 AMERICAN AS A SECOND LANGUAGE 
</HEADLINE>
  &HT;    These articles (described in more detail below) can be purchased
individually by non-clients by contacting Nirdi Relis at (212)
499-3333, or fax her at (212) 499-3382. She also has information on
