   NY-BANK-IPO (Cohoes, N.Y.) _ Cohoes Savings Bank hopes to raise
$59.5 million to $80.5 million through its initial offering of
stock and may use the money to build new branches or purchase other
financial service firms. By CLAIRE HUGHES.
