is recovering from rape and an attempted suicide, all of which
leaves her a bit unbalanced. In one of her realities, she is a
murder-for-hire. In another, she is newly married, on a Jamaican
honeymoon with her husband (William Baldwin), who is trying to help
her recover. Which reality is real? By JEFF MILLAR.
