<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-04 14:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3343 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CENSUS-DATA-ART-BOS &LR;      12-04 1034
