cannot be solved by any system short of a playoff. By Mark
Blaudschun.
</P>
<P>
   BKC-NOTEBOOK (Undated) -- The No. 1 team in men's college
basketball is UConn. The No. 1 team in women's college basketball
is ... UConn. By Mark Blaudschun.
</P>
<P>
   TV-SPORTS-COLUMN (Undated) -- Just when you thought referee
bashing was over, Sunday's NFL pregame shows will put the officials
under even more scrutiny. By Howard Manly.
</P>
<P>
   RAC-COLUMN (Undated) -- It was all Bob Baffert all weekend as
Churchill Downs concluded its lucrative meeting over the
Thanksgiving Holidays. By Ron Indrisano.
</P>
