charities ``from the heart.'' But be sure to use your mind also to
avoid wasting your money. Bitten by the holiday spirit, many people
are more free with their money, and solicitors _ honest and
dishonest _ know this. Americans annually give more than $100
billion to charities and other non-profit groups _ and about $1
billion goes to frauds. (Tharpe, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
