top of the heap of popular electronic encyclopedias since its first
appearance, and the 1999 edition will not lose that place. (Warner,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   CYBER _ ATLANTA _ You won't be surprised to learn that the North
Pole is wired with the latest in T3 high speed data lines and the
finest and most powerful of servers. Santa Claus, after all, does
not mess around Husted, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
