   HOLIDAYS-STRESS &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ Holiday bliss or the same old annual anxiety? What
with church pageants, school plays, visits from cheek-pinching
relatives and the pressures of dividing time between different
members of families that have split, what should be a time of great
cheer often becomes extremely stressful for children. By GRACIE
BONDS STAPLES. Story has moved in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
