<P>
   &UR; NATIONAL (a) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   SODOMY-LAWS (Washington) -- New hopes and obstacles in path of
the national movement to overturn sodomy laws in the 19 states that
still have them. By Mitchell Zuckoff. 1500 words.
</P>
<P>
   ICEMAN-WORMS (Undated) -- The Ice Man whose 5,300-year-old mummy
was discovered seven years ago in a glacier, was apparently
medicating himself for an intestinal disease. By Richard A. Knox.
800 words. (a and i coding)
</P>
