<HEADER>
A3947 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HEARSTADVISORY-HNS &LR;      12-04 0038
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HEARSTADVISORY-HNS </SLUG>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
HEARSTadvisory 
 
Friday, Dec. 4, 1998 
 
EDITORS: Eliminate TXESCAPE-FAMILY. TXESCAPE-FAMILY will not move
tonight.
<TEXT>
<P>
