<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-04 18:56 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3970 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-AFRICA-BEERWAR-NYT &LR;      12-04 1031
