<HEADLINE>
MUSEUM TO NOTE FRENCH FAMILY'S CLAIM TO MONET 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (a and i coding)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By WALTER V. ROBINSON  
 c.1998 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
