   CALIF-GAMBLING (Undated) _ An attorney representing California
Indian tribes says the federal government continues to threaten to
seize gaming equipment at reservation casinos despite the passage
of Proposition 5, the November ballot initiative that legalized
video gaming in the casinos. But that initiative faces a challenge
before the state Supreme Court. By KIM COBB. (Already filed.)
