Lockett gets almost starry-eyed as the dozen white plastic tubes
come into clear view not far from the old Sabine Pass lighthouse.
``We've been searching for this for two years,'' he explains. ``And
now we're close to finding two others, too.'' Lockett has located
the Union gunboat USS Dan. By JOHN MAKEIG (Already filed.)
