</P>
<P>
   SOCIAL-SECURITY (Washington) _ The debate over saving Social
Security shifts into high gear at a two-day White House conference
starting Tuesday. Groups are already hardening their positions on
the most controversial alternative _ individual retirement savings
accounts. By DAN FREEDMAN. (Already filed.)
