<HEADLINE>
NEW YORKERS BASK IN RECORD-BREAKING DECEMBER WARMTH 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (subs 10th graf to fix state for Providence)  (ART ADV: Photo is being sent to NYT photo clients. Non-subscribers
can make individual purchase by calling (888) 603-1036 or (888)
346-9867.) 
(bl) 
