<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Decorating with ornaments _ other than on the tree
 &HT;    By Danny C. Flanders
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   &QR;  Hang them from a wreath on the door.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Hang them from a swag or garland draped over a doorway, window
or mantel.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Display collections by grouping finials along the mantel.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Fill a large clear glass bowl with ornaments to create a table
centerpiece.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Cover candlesticks on the mantel with tree-topper ornaments.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Attach ornaments to the bows of gift-wrapped boxes.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Attach small ones to the napkin rings on a dinner table to
give guests a take-home treat.
</P>
